ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in Nunavut (Ukkusiksalik National Park) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN NUNAVUT (UKKUSIKSALIK NATIONAL PARK) ORDER - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of some 20, 558 square kilometres of land for the establishment of the Ukkusiksalik National Park; and (b) the repeal of a similar Withdrawal from Disposal Order made in 2004.
